            "unidentified": "",
            "value": "<p>You know good artisanship when you see it and can wax poetic about crafting techniques and forms.</p><p>You become trained in Crafting and gain a +1 circumstance bonus on all Crafting checks made to @Compendium[pf2e.actionspf2e.Recall Knowledge (Crafting)]{Recall Knowledge}. If you would automatically become trained in Crafting (from your background or class, for example), you instead become trained in a skill of your choice.</p>\n<p>In addition, you gain the @Compendium[pf2e.feats-srd.Crafter's Appraisal]{Crafter's Appraisal} skill feat, enabling you to identify magic items using the Crafting skill.</p>"
